			<div type="transcription">
				<div type="original" xml:lang="yi">
					<pb facs="EHRI-ET-YV3540320_01.jpg" n="1"/>
					<p><placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/594064/svencionys.html">סווענציאַן</placeName> (אויף דער וועג <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/593116/vilnius.html">ווילנא</placeName>
						<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/460413/daugavpils.html">דינאבורג</placeName>)</p>
					<p>דעם 27 סעפטעמבער 1941 יאהר האט מן אַרויס גיפיהרט אַללע אידין פון <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/864522/svencionys.html">סווענציאנער</placeName>
						<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/864522/svencionys.html">קרייז</placeName>: פון די שטעטלך <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/594064/svencionys.html">סווענציאַן</placeName>, נייסווענציאַן, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/601224/adutiskis.html"
							>היידוצישקי</placeName>, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/600195/ceikiniai.html">צייקין</placeName>, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/597026/mielagenai.html">מאליגאַן</placeName>, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/596473/pabrade.html"
							>פאָדבראָדצאָלט</placeName>, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/11299792/daugeliskis.html">דוגילישיקי</placeName>, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/596751/naujasis-daugeliskis.html">ניי דוגילישקי</placeName>, <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/598998/ignalina.html">איגנאלינא</placeName>, און דעם רעשט פון <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/598515/kaltanenai.html">קאלטיניאן</placeName> (דער גרעסטער טייל איז שוין <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532"
							type="subject">אום געקומען</term> דורך די <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_lithuanians">ליטוויש</term>-באנדיטן מיט 6 וואָכן פאר דעם) אומגיפֿאהר בא (6500) זעקס טויזענד פינף הונדערט אלעמען האט מען גיפֿיהרט אויף דעם <q><placeName
								ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-2461" type="camp">פאליגאן</placeName></q> דאס איז 2 קילאמעטער פֿון שטעטל. נאטורליך האבין זיי ניט געזאגט אז מען פֿיהרט זיי <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject"
							>אום</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">ברענגען</term> נור <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">ארבייטן</term> און טאַקע אויפֿן 2-טן טאג האט מן גענומען זיי אויף <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">אַרביייט</term> אין שטעטל. מען האט אפילו גינומן פֿאריכטן די <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837" type="subject">באראקעס</term> אין <placeName
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-2461" type="camp">פאליגאָן</placeName>. גלייכצייטיג האבן זיי גענומען אַרויס לאזין אידין פון שטאט <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/594064/svencionys.html">סווענציאני</placeName> אַלעס <q>נוטצליכע אידן</q> דיא
						האט פערשטארקט די האפֿנונג באַ אלעמן אַז מען וועט לעבן לאָזן, ווייל איטליכער נוצלעכער איד ד.ה. אשוסטער, שניידער, דאקטאר א. א. וו. האט גיקענט אויך מיט מיט נעהמען די גאנצע <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">פֿאמיליע</term> מיט זיך
						אין <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/594064/svencionys.html">סווענציאַן</placeName> אין <q><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-545" type="subject">געהטא</term></q> וואס איז שוין גיווען פֿאַרויס בעשטימט. דעם ערסטן אקטאבר האבן די באנדיטן <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-411" type="subject">אויס</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-411" type="subject">געקליבן</term> די שטארקסטע <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-826" type="subject">מענער</term> אויף <q><term
								ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">ארבייט</term></q>. זיי זיינען שוין צוריק ניט געקומען, אבער גלייכצייטיג בייַ דעם טויער האט מען גיהאלטן באַן אַרויס לאזין די אידען וועלכע זיינען געווען אַנערקענט אלעס ˶נוטצלעכע̋. אין דערזעלבער
						צייט האט מען גיטריבן צו <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-2461" type="camp">פאליגאן</placeName> פון ניי סווענציאן גראָבן לאַנגע <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-748" type="subject">גרובער</term> דארטן אין
							<placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-2461" type="camp">פאליגאן</placeName> האבען שוין די אידין גיוואוסט אַז מען וועט <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">אויס</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">שיסן</term> נאר דער <q><placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-2461" type="camp">פאליגאן</placeName></q> איז שוין גיווען שטאַרק בעוואַכט מיט <term
							ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_lithuanians">ליטווישע</term> באַנדיטן, וועלכע מען האט געבראַכט פון גאנצען קרייז. דעם 8-טן אקטאבר איז שוין <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">אויס גיווען געשאסן</term> אַללע אידן פון <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/864522/svencionys.html">סווענציאַנער קרייז</placeName>, פון אַ באנדיט איז מיר נאר דאס בעוואוסט אַז דער <term ref="#EHRI-ET-YV3540320_1" rend="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-756" type="subject">רַב</term> פון <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/594064/svencionys.html">סווענציאַן</placeName> איז <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">אום גיקומען</term> אין <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-756" type="subject"
							>תַלית</term>. דער <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-756" type="subject">רַב</term> פון <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/598998/ignalina.html">איגנאלינא</placeName> וועלכער איז גיווען שטאַרק קראַנק הַרַב <persName
							ref="#ehri_et_hayat_moyshe_aharon">ר' משה אהרן חַיט</persName> איהם האבן זיי אויך גיטריבן צום <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-748" type="subject">גרוב</term>. קיינער האט קיין <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-212"
							type="subject">ווידערשטאנד</term> גישטעלט, נור איינער <persName ref="#ehri_et_gendtz_borukh_sholem">ברוך שלום גענדץ</persName> פון <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/594064/svencionys.html">סווענציאן</placeName> דער איז ניט געגאנגען צום <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-748" type="subject">גרוב</term> אויף איהם האבן די באַנדיטן <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">אגראנאַט גיווארפין</term> נאר איינער <persName ref="#ehri_et_murasken"
							>מוראַסקען</persName> אַ פֿריזיר דער האט אקורצע רעדע גיהאלטן אַז אויף אייך באנדיטן וועט אסוף קומען פאר... און ניט לאזענדיג איהם ענדיגין ריידן האט מען <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">דער שאָסן</term> ...</p>
					<p><pb facs="EHRI-ET-YV3540320_02.jpg" n="2"/></p>
					<p>(.... <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/594064/svencionys.html">סווענציאַן</placeName>)</p>
					<p>דיא <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-748" type="subject">גרובער</term> האט מען נור עטוואס מיט ערד צוגידעקט און גילאזין ביז אַפריל מאַנאט 1942 כמעט וויא אָפען דורך דעם ווייסן און געלען זאמד האט דורך גישלאגין די בלוט פון די קדושים און אויך אין
						אייניגע ערטער האבן די וועלף וועלכע איז פֿיל אין דעם געגענד זיי האבן צו פֿרעסן אייניגע <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-515" type="subject">קערפערס</term>. ענדע אַפריל האט מען גיבראַכט <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1057" type="subject">ארבייטער</term> אידישע פון ווילנער ˶געהטא̋ און מען האט די <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-748" type="subject">גרובער</term> מיט (וואַפנע) מיט <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-574" type="subject">קאַלק פערשטאטן און צו גידעקט מיט אַ דיקן שיכט ערד</term> און דעם אָרט אַרום גיצוימט. צו ערסט זיינען דאָ גיווען אַ 60 אידישע <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1057"
							type="subject">אַרבייטער</term> וועלכע האבן נאך דעם פארענדיגן זייער <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">אַרבייט</term> אויף <q><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-2461" type="subject"
							>פאָליגאן</term></q> זיינען זיי גיווען <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">בעשעפֿטיגט</term> באַן האַקען האלץ און אויפֿן באַהן-ליניע. אין אקורצע צייט אַרום ענדע מאיי 1942 האט מן גענומן נייע <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1057" type="subject">אַרבייטער</term> פון <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_ghettos-1103" type="ghetto">סווענציאנער</placeName>
						<placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_ghettos-1103" type="ghetto">געהטא</placeName> עס האבן שוין <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">געארבייט</term> איבער הונדערט <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1057" type="subject">אַרבייטער</term> דאס האט גידויערט ביז ענדע מאַרס מאנאט 1943. מען האט זיי דאַן אַלעמען אפ געשיקט אין <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_ghettos-1103" type="ghetto"
							>סוווענציאנער</placeName>
						<placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_ghettos-1103" type="ghetto">געהטא</placeName> און דאַן האט מען די גאַנצע <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-545" type="subject">געהטא</term> פערטיילט אין 2 גרופעס: איין גרופע אט די וועלכע
						האבן אין <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/593116/vilnius.html">ווילנא</placeName> גיהאט נאהענטע פֿריינד האט מען אפ גישיקט נאך <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/593116/vilnius.html">ווילנא</placeName> די 2 גרופֿפע האט מען געפֿיהרט נאך... <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/598316/kaunas.html">קאָוונע</placeName> און אַרום פאהרענדיג פון <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/593116/vilnius.html">ווילנא</placeName> האט מען זיי דערפֿיהרט עטליכע קילאמעטר צום <q><placeName
								ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-2461" type="camp">פאליגאן</placeName></q> און האט די <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-940" type="subject">וואגאנעס</term> אויף גימאכט דיא מענטשן האבן גלייך פערשטאנען <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-519" type="subject">וואו מען פֿיהרט</term> זיי און האט גינומען <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">שיסן</term> פון מאשינען גיוועהר אללע זיינען <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">אום גיקומען</term> נאר איינצעלנע האבן זיך גיראטעוועט אין יענעם מאמענט איינער פון די געראטעוועטע איז געווען <persName ref="#ehri_et_dibinsky">דיבינסקי</persName> פון <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/598998/ignalina.html">איגנאלינא</placeName> ( <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">אום גיקומען</term> אין ענדע 43-טן יאהר באַ <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/598998/ignalina.html"
							>איגנאלינא</placeName> איינער זיינער אַ חבר פון <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/598098/klaipeda.html">קלייפעדע</placeName> זיין נאמען איז מיר ניט בעואוּסט ).</p>
					<p><placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2867714/munich.html">מיונכען</placeName> 9/xii 46 <persName ref="#ehri_et_kork_yerachmiel">ירחמיאל קאָרק</persName></p>
					<p>געבוירען אין <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/595026/salakas.html">סאלאק</placeName> גיוואונט אין <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/598998/ignalina.html">איגנאלינא</placeName>
						<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/864522/svencionys.html">קרייז</placeName>
						<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/864522/svencionys.html">סווענציאן</placeName></p>
				</div>
				<div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
					<pb facs="EHRI-ET-YV3540320_01.jpg" n="1"/>
					<p><placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/594064/svencionys.html">Švenčionys</placeName> (On the way from <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/593116/vilnius.html">Vilna</placeName> to <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/460413/daugavpils.html">Daugavpils</placeName>
							[<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/460413/daugavpils.html">Dinaburg</placeName>])</p>
					<p><date when="1941-09-27">September 27, 1941</date>, they took all the Jews from the <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/864522/svencionys.html">Švenčionys district</placeName>: from the shtetls of <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/594064/svencionys.html"
							>Švenčionys</placeName>, New <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/594064/svencionys.html">Švenčionys</placeName>, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/601224/adutiskis.html">Adutiškis</placeName>, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/600195/ceikiniai.html"
							>Ceikiniai</placeName>, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/597026/mielagenai.html">Mielagėnai</placeName>, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/596473/pabrade.html">Pabradė</placeName>, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/11299792/daugeliskis.html"
							>Daugėliškis</placeName>, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/596751/naujasis-daugeliskis.html">Naujasis Daugėliškis</placeName>, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/598998/ignalina.html">Ignalina</placeName>, and the remainder from <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/598515/kaltanenai.html">Kaltanėnai</placeName> (the largest part had already been <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">murdered</term> by <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_lithuanians"
							>Lithuanian</term>-bandits six weeks previously), around (6,500) six thousand five hundred altogether, they took them to <q><placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-2461" type="camp">Poligon</placeName></q> which is two kilometers from the
						shtetl. Naturally, they did not tell them that they were being taken there to be <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">murdered</term> but rather to <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject"
							>work</term>. And indeed, on the second day they took them to <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">work</term> in the shtetl. They even started repairing the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-837"
							type="subject">barracks</term> in <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-2461" type="camp">Poligon</placeName>. At the same time, they started setting free Jews from the city of <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/594064/svencionys.html"
							>Švenčionys</placeName> as <q>useful Jews.</q> This reinforced the hope among everyone that they would let them live, because each useful Jew, that is a shoemaker, a tailor, a doctor etc., could also take his entire <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">family</term> with him to <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/594064/svencionys.html">Švenčionys</placeName>, to the <q><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-545"
								type="subject">ghetto</term>,</q> which was already determined in advance. On <date when="1941-10-01">October 1</date>, the bandits <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-411" type="subject">selected</term> the strongest <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-826" type="subject">men</term> for <q><term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">work</term>.</q> They did not come back, but at the same time by the door they stopped letting
						out the Jews who were recognized as <q>useful.</q> At the same time they drove [<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1207" type="subject">people</term>] to <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-2461" type="camp"
							>Poligon</placeName> from New <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/594064/svencionys.html">Švenčionys</placeName> to dig <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-748" type="subject">graves</term> there in <placeName
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-2461" type="camp">Poligon</placeName>, the Jews already knew that they will be <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">shot</term> but the <q><placeName
								ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-2461" type="camp">Poligon</placeName></q> was strongly <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-477" type="subject">guarded</term> by <term ref="#ehri_et_nationalities_lithuanians"
							>Lithuanian</term> bandits, who were brought in from the entire district. On <date when="1941-10-08">October 8</date>, all the Jews from the <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/864522/svencionys.html">Švenčionys district</placeName> had already been <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">shot</term>. I learned from a bandit that the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-756" type="subject">Rabbi</term> from <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/594064/svencionys.html">Švenčionys</placeName> was <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">killed</term> in his <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-756" type="subject">prayer
							shawl</term>. The <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-756" type="subject">Rabbi</term> from <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/598998/ignalina.html">Ignalina</placeName>, who was very <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-292" type="subject">ill</term>, the <persName ref="#ehri_et_hayat_moyshe_aharon">Rabbi Moyshe Aharon Hayat</persName>, they also forced him to the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-748"
							type="subject">grave</term>. No one put up any <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-212" type="subject">resistance</term>, but one <persName ref="#ehri_et_gendtz_borukh_sholem">Borukh Sholem Gendtz</persName> from <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/594064/svencionys.html">Švenčionys</placeName> did not go to the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-748" type="subject">grave</term> and the bandits threw a <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">grenade</term> at him. One <persName ref="#ehri_et_murasken">Murasken</persName>, a hairdresser, gave a short speech, saying that an evil end would come upon you bandits… and without letting him
						finish his speech they <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">shot</term> him...</p>
					<p><pb facs="EHRI-ET-YV3540320_02.jpg" n="2"/></p>
					<p>(….<placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/594064/svencionys.html">Švenčionys</placeName>)</p>
					<p>They covered the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-748" type="subject">graves</term> a bit with earth and left them almost open until the month of April, the blood of the martyrs forced its way through the white and yellow sand and in a few places
						the wolves, of which there are many in the district, ate a number of <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-515" type="subject">bodies</term>. At the end of <date when="1942-04">April</date> they brought Jewish <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1057" type="subject">workers</term> from the <q><placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_ghettos-319" type="ghetto">Vilna ghetto</placeName></q> and they covered the <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-748" type="subject">graves</term> with (slaked lime) <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-574" type="subject">chalk and a thick layer of earth</term> and the place was fenced off. At first
						there were around sixty Jewish <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1057" type="subject">workers</term> who, after finishing their <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">work</term> at <q><placeName
								ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-2461" type="camp">Poligon</placeName>,</q> they were occupied with chopping wood and <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">working</term> on the railway line. In a
						short time, around the end of <date when="1942-05">May 1942</date>, they brought new <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1057" type="subject">workers</term> from <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_ghettos-1103" type="ghetto"
							>Švenčionys ghetto</placeName>. There were already more than a hundred <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1057" type="subject">workers</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-943" type="subject">laboring</term> there. This lasted until the end of <date when="1943-03">March 1943</date>. Then they sent them all to the <placeName
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_ghettos-1103" type="ghetto">ghetto of Švenčionys</placeName> and they divided the entire <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-545" type="subject">ghetto</term> into two groups: in one group were
						those with friends or relatives in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/593116/vilnius.html">Vilna</placeName>, they were sent to <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/593116/vilnius.html">Vilna</placeName>. The two groups were taken to… <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/598316/kaunas.html">Kovno</placeName>. And leaving <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/593116/vilnius.html">Vilna</placeName> they took them a few kilometers to <q><placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-2461"
								type="camp">Poligon</placeName></q> and opened the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-940" type="subject">wagons</term>. Then the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1207" type="subject">people</term> straight away
						understood to where they <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-519" type="subject">had been taken</term>. They began <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">shooting</term> with machine guns, all were <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-532" type="subject">murdered</term>, apart from a few who saved themselves in that moment. One of those who were saved was <persName ref="#ehri_et_dibinsky">Dibinsky</persName> from <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/598998/ignalina.html">Ignalina</placeName> (he was <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-132" type="subject">killed</term> at the end of <date when="1943">1943</date> near <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/598998/ignalina.html">Ignalina</placeName>, a friend of his from <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/598098/klaipeda.html">Klaipeda</placeName>, I do not know his name).</p>
					<p><placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2867714/munich.html">Munich</placeName>
						<date when="1946-12-09">9/12/1946</date></p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_et_kork_yerachmiel">Yerachmiel Kork</persName></p>
					<p>Born in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/595026/salakas.html">Salakas</placeName>, lived in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/598998/ignalina.html">Ignalina</placeName>, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/594064/svencionys.html">Švenčionys</placeName>
						district.</p>
